ildItem_1","label":"ggB9Gp8U8JQ_childItem_1","default":"<p>Why not just use water?</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggB9Gp8U8JQ_childItem_2","label":"ggB9Gp8U8JQ_childItem_2","default":"<p>How to use it</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggB9Gp8U8JQ_childItem_3","label":"ggB9Gp8U8JQ_childItem_3","default":"<p>Pro tip</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggB9Gp8U8JQ_childItem_4","label":"ggB9Gp8U8JQ_childItem_4","default":"<p>Key Ingredients</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggB9Gp8U8JQ_childItem_5","label":"ggB9Gp8U8JQ_childItem_5","default":"<p>Will it dry my skin out?</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggB9Gp8U8JQ_childItem_6","label":"ggB9Gp8U8JQ_childItem_6","default":"<p>Shipping</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggB9Gp8U8JQ_childItem_7","label":"ggB9Gp8U8JQ_childItem_7","default":"<p>60-Day “Try It” Guarantee</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggKZrkCgfQz_text","label":"ggKZrkCgfQz_text","default":"<p>Men who want their face actually clean and ready for whatever they’re putting on next.</p><p>This washes off dirt, oil, sweat, and buildup<br>so your cream or serum can actually do its job.</p><p>Works for all skin types.<br>Dry. Oily. Somewhere in between.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggLuQ0nuQN8_text","label":"ggLuQ0nuQN8_text","default":"<p>Because water doesn’t cut it.</p><p>Water won’t remove oil, pollution, dead skin, or the junk your face collects all day.</p><p>A real cleanser does.</p><p>Clean skin absorbs products better.<br>Which means better results. Faster.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggR8kqovO2L_text","label":"ggR8kqovO2L_text","default":"<p><strong>Step 1:</strong><br>2–3 pumps on a wet face</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Step 2:</strong><br>Rub in with circular motions</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Step 3:</strong><br>Rinse. Dry off. Done.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggFipoBsWwP_text","label":"ggFipoBsWwP_text","default":"<p>Use it before shaving.</p><p>It softens your skin and facial hair so the razor glides easier.<br>Less irritation. Cleaner shave.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggNgskm7d42_text","label":"ggNgskm7d42_text","default":"<p><strong>Niacinamide</strong><br>Helps improve skin elasticity.<br>Reduces excess pigment.<br>Helps fade dark spots.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Chamomile</strong><br>Calms irritated skin.<br>Great after shaving.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Sodium Hyaluronate</strong><br>Helps your skin hold onto moisture — even after you rinse.<br>So you feel clean. Not dried out.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggg59nFYXJE_text","label":"ggg59nFYXJE_text","default":"<p>No</p><p>Unlike basic bar soap, this doesn’t strip your skin raw.</p><p>Niacinamide and Chamomile help keep your skin balanced and comfortable.</p><p>Clean — not tight.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggWWrnyOmWZ_text","label":"ggWWrnyOmWZ_text","default":"<p>Ships in 24–48 hours from our Italian warehouse.<br>Free shipping on orders over €50.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggz0FAMQkBP_text","label":"ggz0FAMQkBP_text","default":"<p>You’ve got 60 days to test it.<br>If you don’t like it, email us.<br>You get 100% of your money back.</p>"}],
